1. binary operations : 

A.   odd or even : 

   a & 1 == 1 : odd
   a & 1 != 1 : even

B. 2 numbers have the same sign or not : 

   x ^ y < 0 : opposite signs

   x ^ y >=0 :  the same sign

C.  get negative of a number :  -x == ~x +1

D. add 1 to an integer : 

   ~~x == x +1

E. Swap 2 numbers without using any 3rd variable

http://www.techiedelight.com/bit-hacks-part-1-basic/#P2

 x=x ^ y
 y=x ^ y
 x=x ^ y

F.  kth bit : 1 << (k-1)

